<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= user.name %> </title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        body {
        background: -webkit-linear-gradient(bottom, #610675, #f18af7);
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }
      .btn-outline-dark{
        background-color: rgb(45, 232, 82);
        border-color: green;
      }
      .btn-outline-dark:hover{
        background-color: rgb(5, 103, 25);
        border-color: green;
      }
    </style>
    <link rel="icon" href="https://tamaris.space/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/icon.png" sizes="192x192">
  </head>
  <body>
    <section class="h-100 gradient-custom-2">
      <div class="container py-2 h-100">
        <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center h-100">
          <div class="col col-lg-9 col-xl-7">
            <div class="card">
              <div
                class="rounded-top text-white d-flex flex-row"
                style="background-color: #000; height: 200px"
              >
                <div class="ms-4 mt-5 d-flex flex-column" style="width: 150px">
                    <img src="<%= user.img %>" alt="Generic placeholder image" class="img-fluid img-thumbnail mt-4 mb-2" style="z-index: 1; min-width: 160px; min-height: 160px; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;">

                  <button
                    type="button"
                    class="btn btn-outline-dark"
                    data-mdb-ripple-color="dark"
                    style="z-index: 1"
                  >
                  <a style="text-decoration: none; color: white; font-weight: 700; padding: 20px;" href="https://wa.me/<%= user.phone %>">Whatsapp</a>
                  
                  </button>
                </div>
                <div class="ms-3" style="margin-top: 130px">
                  <h5><%= user.name %>, <%= user.age %> </h5>
                  <p><%= user.input1 %> </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-2 text-black" style="background-color: #f8f9fa">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-end text-center py-1">
                  <div>
                    <p class="mb-1 h5"></p>
                    <p class="small text-muted mb-0"></p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="px-3">
                    <p class="mb-1 h5"></p>
                    <p class="small text-muted mb-0"></p>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="mb-1 h5"></p>
                    <p class="small text-muted mb-0"></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card-body p-4 text-black">
                <div class="mb-1">
                  <p class="lead fw-normal mt-3" style="text-align: center; color: #610675; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0;">معلومات عامة</p>
                  <div class="p-2" style="background-color: #e5ebf0; margin: 0;">
                    <p class="font-italic" style="text-align: center; margin: 0;"><strong> المستوى الدراسي و التخصص</strong><br><%= user.input2 %>  </p>
                    <p class="font-italic" style="text-align: center; margin: 0;"><strong> اذا كنت موظف شنو هي المهنة لي كتزاول</strong><br><%= user.input3 %>  </p>
                    <p class="font-italic" style="text-align: center; margin: 0;"><strong> واش عندك خبرة سابقة فالعمل الجمعوي</strong><br><%= user.input4 %>  </p>
                    <p class="font-italic" style="text-align: center; margin: 0;"><strong> واش عندك اي انتماء سياسي او جمعوي حاليا</strong><br><%= user.input5 %>  </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-2">
                    <p class="lead fw-normal" style="text-align: center; color: #610675; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0;"> عن مقدم الطلب</p>
                    <div class="p-4" style="background-color: #e5ebf0; margin: 0;">
                      <p class="font-italic" style="text-align: center;"><%= user.input6 %> </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </body>
</html>
